Module org.junit.platform.commons
Package org.junit.platform.commons.logging

Interface Logger

  • @API(status=INTERNAL,
     since="1.0")
public interface Logger
    The Logger API serves as a simple logging facade for java.util.logging (JUL).

    1.0
